    contents:
      - text: "The scattered One-Hit Obliterator led you to a\nlocation where a stone monument with a map of\ntrials appeared. Kass's song seems related...\n\nOne, "
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: stop a titan of molten stone
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: ".\nTwo, "
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: follow rings of light alone
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: ".\nThree, "
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: "survive lava's fiery fate"
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: ".\nChampion, trials await!\n\nYou still have "
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: three
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: " trials to complete."
  QL_BalladOfHeroGoron_Finish:
    contents:
      - text: "You defeated the phantasm of Fireblight\nGanon, which was born from your own\nmemories and fears.\n\nKass's composition, entitled "
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: "Champion Daruk's\nSong"
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: ", was so true and moving that it allowed\nyou to visualize a memory from 100 years ago.\n\nBy conquering the trial, your sacred power has\nincreased and Daruk's Protection has become\nmore efficient than ever."
